                                <foliation>Modern foliation in pencil. Intermittent and crossed out foliation in pencil by a modern hand starting on <locus from="5r" to="5r" scheme="folios"/>.</foliation>
                                <collation>
                                    <formula>1(1+1+1+1), 2-19(12), 20(2+2+2). Collation of quires 1 and 20 tentative.</formula>
